<div class="title">Extreme Mellowness</div>
<div class="substance">Wormwood & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=AuralChaos&Exact=1">AuralChaos</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; AuralChaos. "Extreme Mellowness: An Experience with Wormwood & Alcohol (exp7988)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 15, 2001. erowid.org/exp/7988</div>

